ortedly-build-a-dedicated-passwords-app-for-the-iphone-and-mac-211812245.html"><ins>build its own password manager for iOS and macOS</ins></a> .该公司已经内置了一个复杂的密码管理器，但是有传言称独立应用程序将既易于使用又更大。 If true, it&#39;s likely to prompt fears that third-party password managers, like 1Password and LastPass, are at risk of being muscled out of the space.</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-will-reportedly-build-a-dedicated-passwords-app-for-the-iphone-and-mac-211812245.html"><strong><ins>继续阅读。</ins></strong></a></p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-what-to-expect-from-apples-big-event-111524145.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-what-to-expect-from-apples-big-event-111524145.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 90d9f2b1-2305-420e-a6b4-a9a2def8e5ec</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Daniel Cooper]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 07 Jun 2024 11:15:24 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1717754134</ingested><modified> 2024-06-07T09:55:39+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Daniel Cooper]]></category><media:content height="899" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-02%2F1711a270-db12-11ee-86ce-4a7693cc0a77&amp;resize=1400%2C899&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=e55a3e1fb4793888b37885fe1dcd81a1f6a43fed" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></med